UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. Clarence E. TUNNELL, Appellee. No. 6732. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Jan. 25, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and MeCORMICK, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
